intent.user_query: Which product categories have the lowest stock levels (sum of StockQuantity), and what is their average price?

phases.goal: Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT p.ProductType, SUM(p.StockQuantity) AS TotalStock, AVG(p.Price) AS AveragePrice FROM fitness_db.Products p GROUP BY p.ProductType ORDER BY TotalStock ASC;

arguments.sql: SELECT p.ProductType, SUM(p.StockQuantity) AS TotalStock, AVG(p.Price) AS AveragePrice FROM fitness_db.Products p GROUP BY p.ProductType ORDER BY TotalStock ASC;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
